Herbie Mann - Reggae (1974) (320kbps)

Great jazz album from flautist Herbie Mann and his crew.

Reached #14 on "Billboard Jazz Album" chart, and #141 on "The Billboard 200" chart, in 1974.

Reissued by Wounded Bird in 2001, and Rhino in 2005.
